query:
SELECT 
  DATE(date) as entry_date,
  COUNT(*) as entries_count,
  SUM(durationHours) / 100 as total_hours
FROM timeEntries 
WHERE userId = (SELECT id FROM users WHERE openId LIKE '%vikram%' LIMIT 1)
  AND date >= '2025-10-01' 
  AND date < '2025-11-01'
GROUP BY DATE(date)
ORDER BY entry_date DESC;
